    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "深刻そうな雰囲気だな。一体どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem pretty serious. What's going on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "私はアイドルが好き……\nアイドルの知識なら誰にも負けない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I love idols…\nThere's no one who knows more about idols than me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "だから、トリエルとリズノワが移籍して来た時……\n凄くワクワクした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ when TRINITYAiLE and LizNoir transferred here…\nI was really excited…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと憧れてたから……最初は話すのも緊張した……\nでも、一緒に練習したり……ライブで共演したり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because I've admired them for so long…At first‚ even talking to them made me nervous…\nBut practicing together… performing together in live shows…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "憧れのアイドルと交流することで……\n私も成長出来た……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By interacting with the idols I admired…\nI was able to grow too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "つまり……私が言いたいのは、そういうこと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… Thats what I wanted to say…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
